Package think.rpgitems.power.impl

Class ProjectilePower

  • java.lang.Object
    • think.rpgitems.power.BasePropertyHolder
      • think.rpgitems.power.impl.BasePower
        • think.rpgitems.power.impl.ProjectilePower
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Power, PropertyHolder
    public class ProjectilePower
extends BasePower
    Power projectile.

    Launches projectile of type projectileType with gravity when right clicked. If use isCone mode, amount of projectiles will randomly distributed in the cone with angle range centered with player's direction.
